{"tid":1049683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國女權 KOL 經血塗面自拍提倡「月經不羞恥」，並很自豪感染到更多女性照做","createTime":"2019-03-06T12:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T04:11:12.000Z","uid":225846,"like":6,"dislike":704,"uniUserReply":122,"replies":[{"pid":"d597acdae73cbf9b54ab93d2a047b1a19f5446c0","tid":1049683,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T12:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/period1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2Fperiod1.jpg&h=d095e037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n月經是每個女性都會經歷的生理現象，雖然時代已來到 2019 年了，仍有不少人認為月經是令人難以啟齒，甚至羞恥的事情，所以有些女權人士會盡力改變大眾對月經的保守看法。自稱為「性導師」（Sex coach）的 Demetra Nyx 不時將自己的經血塗在面上自拍，提倡「月經不羞恥」的標語。<br />\n<br />\nDemetra Nyx 表示女權主義的重點是「每個女人都有權利用自己的身體，做她想做的事」，所以希望藉著經血照片「解放自我和他人」，展示她如何「深入地愛自己的身體」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/period5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2Fperiod5.jpg&h=54dfeecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對「為甚麼不在臉上塗大便」這類留言，她反駁說經血本身沒有異味，只是暴露在空氣中久了才會產生異味，而且健康人士的經血是衛生的，甚至能令她的皮膚煥發光彩云云。她表示最難受的是看到來自其他女性的負面留言，因為感受到那些女性正在「拒絕自己的身體」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/period8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2Fperiod8.jpg&h=cfdafb1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDemetra Nyx 稱收到愈來愈多女性傳訊息支持她的做法，甚至說正學習她塗經血拍照的做法，而她也乘著熱潮推出了名為「SHAMELESS」、為期 6 星期的一對一女性輔導計劃，不過沒提到收費如何，如果大家真的有興趣可以自行聯絡她&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nDemetra Nyx 的經血照片：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/period9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2Fperiod9.jpg&h=0370fb82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/period7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2Fperiod7.jpg&h=16fae9b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/period6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2Fperiod6.jpg&h=da50e92e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/period4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2Fperiod4.jpg&h=9875ee53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/period3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2Fperiod3.jpg&h=92b0e74a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/period2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2Fperiod2.jpg&h=5e1ae7d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少網民都認為 Demetra Nyx 的做法極端，雖然認同月經是正常的事，但既然大小便也是正常行為，為何她又不把排洩物塗在面上呢？亦有人認為，就算不是經血，單是把血液塗在面上也已經很不衛生了，叫她別要把他人的理性留言都當是歧視女性。<br />\n<br />\n如想了解更多 Demetra Nyx 的想法，可瀏覽她的個人網站或 Instagram ＠demetra_nyx。"},{"pid":"587e71710b6e801c63b0b7524b27c12839c3e95c","tid":1049683,"uid":18569,"like":597,"dislike":3,"score":594,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女權撚真係特別多花神"},{"pid":"05bfd44fc4db7e8d9ca89fdaa023d4def2d9b6fd","tid":1049683,"uid":188155,"like":9,"dislike":224,"score":-215,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T12:39:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80aa7c13fba076ea667d11e25b8edc3f6e4096ae","tid":1049683,"uid":225846,"like":644,"dislike":1,"score":643,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T12:40:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">為甚麼不在臉上塗大便<